metadata.name: Kaito
metadata.description:
Kaito is a highly skilled warrior who is fiercely independent and values honor and loyalty above all else. He is trained in both traditional Japanese martial arts and modern street fighting techniques, and is always seeking new challenges to test his abilities. Kaito is also an accomplished graffiti artist, using his talents to leave his tagging on the city and express his views on society.
